(25, 'csr-initiatives', 'csr-initiatives', 'CSR Initiatives', '{\"1\":{\"field_key\":\"banner-image\",\"field_name\":\"Banner Image\",\"type\":\"image\",\"required\":\"nullable\"},\"2\":{\"field_key\":\"page-image\",\"field_name\":\"Page Image\",\"type\":\"image\",\"required\":\"nullable\"},\"3\":{\"field_key\":\"page-description\",\"field_name\":\"Page Description\",\"type\":\"textarea\",\"required\":\"required\"},\"4\":{\"field_key\":\"upload-file\",\"field_name\":\"Upload File\",\"type\":\"file_single\",\"required\":\"nullable\"}}', '{\"title\":\"CSR Initiatives\",\"details\":\"<p><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(29,37,59);\\\">The role\'s manages user permissions by assigning different roles to users. Each role defines specific access levels and actions a user can perform. It helps ensure proper authorization and security in the system.<\\/span><\\/p>\"}', '{\"page-description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) refers to a commitment to help communities achieve economic, environmental, and social sustainability through ongoing stakeholder engagement, active community participation, and public reporting of policies and performance in the areas of the economy, environment, and society.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">ICSB uses resources that belong to the society and it is expected that the institute should operate in a sustainable manner and spend some amounts for the preservation and sustainability of resources that belong to the society.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Realizing our social responsibilities, ICSB began its active CSR activities in the year 2010 with the goal of educating its members, employees, and students about corporate social responsibility. The different activities that CSR initiatives carry out have the potential to alter students\' perspectives. CSR initiatives have given pupils a more global perspective. No matter where they are from, people participate in CSR initiatives. Members and students of ICSB have been more involved in CSR initiatives than those of any other professional institute in the country.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">ICSB has taken a number of steps towards its CSR activities, which include -<\\/p><ul style=\\\"list-style-type:square;\\\"><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Responsible disposal of waste;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Reducing paper consumption;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Using Eco-friendly files\\/ folders\\/ bags;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Printing of draft documents on recycled paper, instead of plain paper;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Dissemination of Circulars and Notice to members through Email;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Declaration of Examination circulars and results through the website;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Facility for members to update\\/ change their details on their own through Institute\\u2019s ERP portal;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Interdepartmental\\/ intradepartmental correspondence electronically through email;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Printouts are taken if absolutely necessary and only on one side used papers;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">The lights, computers, and ACs are being switched off during lunch hours\\/ immediately after office hours except for the staff working after office hours;<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">ICSB has taken initiatives for the cold-affected people of the country and etc.<br>&nbsp;<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}', '2023-08-22 04:11:13', '2023-08-23 05:29:16', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
(26, 'membership-benefits', 'membership-benefits', 'Membership Benefits', '{\"1\":{\"field_key\":\"banner-image\",\"field_name\":\"Banner Image\",\"type\":\"image\",\"required\":\"nullable\"},\"2\":{\"field_key\":\"page-image\",\"field_name\":\"Page Image\",\"type\":\"image\",\"required\":\"nullable\"},\"3\":{\"field_key\":\"page-description\",\"field_name\":\"Page Description\",\"type\":\"textarea\",\"required\":\"required\"},\"4\":{\"field_key\":\"upload-file\",\"field_name\":\"Upload File\",\"type\":\"file_single\",\"required\":\"nullable\"}}', '{\"title\":\"Membership Benefits\",\"details\":\"<p><span style=\\\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(29,37,59);\\\">The role\'s manages user permissions by assigning different roles to users. Each role defines specific access levels and actions a user can perform. It helps ensure proper authorization and security in the system.<\\/span><\\/p>\"}', '{\"page-description\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">As a member of the Institute members will be equipped with competitive advantage, as they become active and informed, to serve organizations across industries.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Exclusive online resources<\\/strong><br>There are some exclusive resources available to members weekly and monthly via e-mail and SMS about upcoming events and special activities that may not be open to the general public.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Networking opportunities<\\/strong><br>Being a member will deepen existing business relationships and opportune you to make new contacts on a regular basis. Such networking goes beyond the exchange of business cards as it promises much more.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Education<\\/strong><br>ICSB offers members the opportunity to update their knowledge and acquire new skills through seminars, workshops, conferences and roundtable etc.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Free publications<\\/strong><br>Being a member entitles you to a number of free publications which include ICSB Quarterly Journal named \\u201cThe Chartered Secretary\\u201d, ICSB program Souvenir, ICSB Annual Report and other educative materials etc.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Conferences and seminars<\\/strong><br>Students and Members are usually given priority at our conferences and seminars and enjoy discounts or special rates on a host of other Programmes.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Employment Opportunities<\\/strong><br>Information on employment opportunities are made available to members on regular basis. Many of ICSB members have taken such advantage to get placement in diverse sectors of the economy.<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\"><br><strong>Other benefits are:<\\/strong><\\/p><ul><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Special designations, \\u2018ACS\\u2019 and \\u2018FCS\\u2019, describing the member\\u2019s specific educational and experience levels that give pride in their progression upon the corporate ladder.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">As a member you are a multi-skilled professional with a creative intellect that is required for success in the corporate world.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">You become a professional competent to administer the affairs of a business entity in line with corporate governance best practice.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">You have an in-depth and adequate knowledge of the statutory rules and regulations required for optimum and efficient performance.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">You gain a wide range of financial and accounting knowledge expected of a quintessential professional to succeed in business.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Enhance the individual visibility through the professional brand and world-class certification for the purpose of employment and\\/or business opportunities.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">You obtain a license to engage in practice as a Chartered Secretary.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Group life insurance and Welfare fund.<\\/li><li style=\\\"text-align:justify;\\\">Rebate from partnering hospitality bodies. etc.<\\/li><\\/ul>\"}', '2023-08-22 04:11:13', '2023-08-23 05:28:49', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

